## Sample Output (Ví dụ output của prompt trên)

**Input lyrics:**
```
[VERSE 1]
I sat where I always sit
I scrolled through names I never call
The silence wasn't empty — it was full of all the things I couldn't say

[CHORUS]
Even if I don't feel it
Even if I don't pray it right
Someone stays
And that is grace

[VERSE 2]  
I walked with You through autumn fields
The leaves fell slow like golden prayers

[BRIDGE]
You didn't fix the broken parts
You sat beside them in the dark
And called them beautiful

[OUTRO]
(instrumental)
```

**Output:**
```
