[NOTE] ESTABLISHING — Cold open. Meditative entry into the felt world. Intensity 1

// SHOT 02 | 5s | MS
[BGM] Piano begins — sparse, melancholic, rubato
[SFX] Soft felt footsteps on wooden floor, backpack rustling
[NARRATOR] I sat where I always sit / I scrolled through names I never call
[CAM] Static wide — black sheep sitting alone at oversized wooden table, other chairs empty. Sheep packs small felt backpack
[VFX] Cool palette, muted morning light. Sheep takes up 15% of frame — tiny in vast empty dining area. Slow-motion 80%
[NOTE] VERSE 1 — STRUGGLE. emotional_match: lyrics = social isolation → visual = physical isolation at empty table. Jesus NOT present. Intensity 2

// SHOT 03 | 6s | WS
[SFX] Schoolyard laughter (distant), felt grass crunching under small hooves
[NARRATOR] The silence wasn't empty — it was full of all the things I couldn't say
[CAM] Tracking pan L→R following black sheep walking alone on felt path. White sheep flock visible in background, clustered together laughing
[VFX] Overcast cool lighting. Black sheep small at left third, white flock at right third — visual gap between them. Rim light only on black sheep's fuzzy edges
[NOTE] VERSE 1 — STRUGGLE. narrative_parallel: "silence full of unsaid things" → sheep walks past group that excludes it. High angle over sheep = vulnerability. Intensity 3

// SHOT 04 | 5s | CU
[SFX] Single clear resin teardrop sound
[NARRATOR] (piano sustain — phrase ending breath)
[CAM] Slow zoom in — close-up on black sheep's face. Two resin teardrops on fuzzy felt cheeks. Black bead eyes reflecting single point of light
[VFX] Shallow DoF maximum, blurred cool background. Rim light catching individual wool fibers around eyes. Slow-motion tears
[NOTE] VERSE 1 — EMOTIONAL PEAK of struggle. Intensity 4. Pause at phrase ending — let the weight land

// SHOT 05 | 6s | WS
[BGM] Music lifts — guitar chord enters, warmth into the mix. Key shift approaching major
[SFX] Warm wind, distant chime bell
[NARRATOR] Even if I don't feel it / Even if I don't pray it right
[CAM] Wide shot — sheep standing at edge of dark felt forest, looking back. Behind sheep: darkness. Ahead: a warm golden light emerging through the trees
[VFX] SPLIT LIGHTING — left half of frame is cool/dark (forest), right half is warm/golden (clearing). God rays beginning to appear through tree gaps. Magical transition moment
[NOTE] CHORUS — THE TURNING POINT begins. Lyrics mention "don't feel it" → sheep at the literal threshold between darkness and light. Intensity 3

// SHOT 06 | 5s | MS
[BGM] Full guitar swell — acoustic, warm, open chord
[SFX] Soft footstep on felt grass, birds beginning to sing
[NARRATOR] Someone stays
[CAM] Medium shot — Jesus figure steps into frame from the golden light. Warm rim light explodes around his wool tunic edges. Hand extended toward sheep
[VFX] Full warm palette. God rays behind Jesus creating silhouette halo. Bloom 20% around light source. Fireflies appearing. Slow-motion 80%
[NOTE] CHORUS — JESUS APPEARS. "Someone stays" = Jesus physically arrives. metaphor_translation: abstract "someone" → concrete needle-felted Jesus figure. Low angle on Jesus. Intensity 4

// SHOT 07 | 5s | MCU
[NARRATOR] And that is grace
[CAM] MCU — Jesus kneeling to sheep's eye level. Gentle felted hand on sheep's head. Both in warm light
[VFX] Maximum warmth. Rim light on both characters' fuzzy edges. Golden dust motes floating. Tears on sheep catching warm light now (relief tears, not sad tears)
[NOTE] CHORUS — RESOLUTION of turning point. "Grace" = the physical act of Jesus coming down to sheep's level. Intensity 5

// SHOT 08 | 5s | WS
[BGM] Gentle acoustic guitar continuing, pastoral, warm
[SFX] Crunching autumn leaves under feet, gentle wind through felt trees
[NARRATOR] I walked with You through autumn fields
[CAM] Tracking pan L→R — Jesus and sheep walking together through autumn felt forest. Golden/orange felt leaves falling in slow-motion
[VFX] Full warm autumn palette (#D4870E, #8B4513). Leaves = tiny cut felt pieces falling at 80% speed. Both characters occupy 40% of frame — together, connected. Atmospheric perspective on background
[NOTE] VERSE 2 — THE JOURNEY TOGETHER. Walking montage begins. Literal walking = spiritual journey forward. Intensity 3

// SHOT 09 | 6s | MS
[SFX] Leaves landing softly on felt grass, distant bird song
[NARRATOR] The leaves fell slow like golden prayers
[CAM] Medium shot — sheep looking up at falling leaves with wonder. Jesus walking beside, one hand on sheep's back. Leaves floating down around both
[VFX] Golden hour backlighting. Each falling felt leaf catches rim light = "golden prayers" made literal. Heavy slow-motion on leaves (70% speed). Dreamy bokeh background
[NOTE] VERSE 2 — JOURNEY. symbolic: "golden prayers" = golden leaves catching light. Beautiful metaphor made visual. Intensity 3

// SHOT 10 | 6s | CU
[BGM] Music becomes intimate — piano solo returns, softer, major key now. Cello enters with warm sustained note
[SFX] Soft crackling fire, night insects, owl hoot (gentle)
[NARRATOR] You didn't fix the broken parts
