[VFX] Warm fire point-light source (#FF8C00). Cave walls are textured felt. Firefly bokeh dots floating. Strong rim light from fire on wool edges. Very dark background = intimacy
[NOTE] BRIDGE — DEEP INTIMACY. narrative_parallel: "didn't fix" → Jesus doesn't doing anything, just BEING PRESENT. Sitting beside, not fixing. This nuance is key. Intensity 4

// SHOT 11 | 5s | ECU
[SFX] Sheep's soft breathing, fire crackling quietly
[NARRATOR] You sat beside them in the dark
[CAM] Extreme close-up — sheep's bead eye reflecting the tiny campfire. Individual wool fibers visible at macro level. Eye half-closed in peace
[VFX] Maximum shallow DoF. Fire reflection in glossy bead eye. Single catchlight becomes warm orange (fire) instead of white. Visible needle-punch texture on felt face
[NOTE] BRIDGE — PEAK INTIMACY. ECU = maximum emotional closeness. "Sat beside them in the dark" = visual shows the dark cave BUT with warm light. Dark is no longer scary. Intensity 5

// SHOT 12 | 5s | MCU
[BGM] Music swells — vocal harmonies enter, full arrangement building
[SFX] Wind chime — single crystalline note
[NARRATOR] And called them beautiful
[CAM] MCU — Jesus looking at sheep with gentle smile. Mouth slightly open as if whispering. Warm golden rim light creating full halo around Jesus's wool edges
[VFX] Full bloom. God rays entering cave from behind Jesus. Maximum warmth. Tears of joy — glowing resin drops
[NOTE] BRIDGE — CLIMAX. "Called them beautiful" = Jesus actively affirming the sheep. This is the emotional peak of the entire video. Intensity 5

// SHOT 13 | 7s | WS
[BGM] Music resolving — instruments fading one by one, final piano note sustaining
[SFX] Gentle wind, distant sheep bells, evening birdsong fading
[NARRATOR] (instrumental — outro)
[CAM] Wide shot — Jesus and sheep sitting together on felt hilltop, watching sunset. Back-lit silhouettes with golden rim light edges. Rolling felt hills stretching to horizon
[VFX] Maximum golden hour. Warm amber (#FFB347). Silhouettes with glowing fuzzy edges. Atmospheric haze in background. Slow-motion grass swaying. Fade to warm black over final 2 seconds
[NOTE] OUTRO — PEACE. Resolution shot. Both characters at rest, facing forward (future). The journey continues but no longer alone. Intensity 4 → fade to 0
```

